<subSubSection pageId="48" pageNumber="363" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="48.[831,1437,1961,2082]" pageId="48" pageNumber="363">
Forty-one species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Moore, 1888" authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1888" box="[1053,1137,1962,1985]" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Patania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="48" pageNumber="363" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1053,1137,1962,1985]" italics="true" pageId="48" pageNumber="363">Patania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from around the world have been described (
<bibRefCitation author="Nuss M. &amp; Landry B. &amp; Vegliante F. &amp; Trankner A. &amp; Mally R. &amp; Hayden J. E. &amp; Bauer F. &amp; Segerer A. &amp; Li H. &amp; Schouten R. &amp; Solis M. A. &amp; Trofimova T. &amp; De Prins J. &amp; Speidel W." box="[1001,1182,1993,2018]" journalOrPublisher="Last accessed" pageId="48" pageNumber="363" pagination="2003 - 2016" part="1" refString="Nuss M., Landry B., Vegliante F., Trankner A., Mally R., Hayden J. E., Bauer F., Segerer A., Li H., Schouten R., Solis M. A., Trofimova T., De Prins J., Speidel W. 2003 - 2016. Global Information System on Pyraloidea. www. pyraloidea. org. Last accessed: 1 June 2016." title="Global Information System on Pyraloidea. www. pyraloidea. org" type="journal article" year="2016">
Nuss 
<emphasis box="[1061,1106,1993,2017]" italics="true" pageId="48" pageNumber="363">et al</emphasis>
., 2016
</bibRefCitation>
). The three species from the 
<collectingRegion box="[869,956,2026,2049]" country="Sri Lanka" name="Western" pageId="48" pageNumber="363">Western</collectingRegion>
Hemisphere (
<bibRefCitation author="Munroe E. G." box="[1102,1255,2025,2050]" editor="Heppner, J. B." journalOrPublisher="Hyblaeoidea - Pyraloidea - Tortricoidea" pageId="48" pageNumber="363" pagination="34 - 79" part="3" refString="Munroe E. G. 1995. Crambidae (Crambinae, Schoenobiinae, Cybalomiinae, Linostinae, Glaphyriinae, Dichogaminae, Scopariinae, Musotiminae, Midilinae, Nymphulinae, Odontiinae, Evergestinae, Pyraustinae). Pp. 34 - 79. In: Heppner, J. B., Atlas of Neotropical Lepidoptera. Checklist: Part 2. Hyblaeoidea - Pyraloidea - Tortricoidea 3. Association for Tropical Lepidoptera &amp; Scientific Publishers, Gainesville." title="Crambidae (Crambinae, Schoenobiinae, Cybalomiinae, Linostinae, Glaphyriinae, Dichogaminae, Scopariinae, Musotiminae, Midilinae, Nymphulinae, Odontiinae, Evergestinae, Pyraustinae). Pp" type="journal article" volumeTitle="Atlas of Neotropical Lepidoptera. Checklist: Part 2" year="1995">Munroe, 1995</bibRefCitation>
) had been placed in 
<taxonomicName authority="Meyrick, 1890" authorityName="Meyrick" authorityYear="1890" box="[859,1143,2057,2082]" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Pleuroptya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="48" pageNumber="363" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" subFamily="Spilomelinae">
<emphasis box="[859,977,2057,2080]" italics="true" pageId="48" pageNumber="363">Pleuroptya</emphasis>
Meyrick, 1890
</taxonomicName>
, a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Moore, 1888" authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1888" box="[1305,1389,2059,2082]" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Patania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="48" pageNumber="363" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1305,1389,2059,2082]" italics="true" pageId="48" pageNumber="363">Patania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
